fields.name: White Casket "Stanford" - Brown Finish with White Interior
fields.description:
The White cremation casket features a handcrafted Teak Veneer Wood in a matte finish. Fully-lined with a plush, ivory velvet interior with a soft matching pillow, this casket is durable, sturdy and elegantly crafted out of the finest materials available. The ivory colored velvet interior  perfectly complements the deep rich outside coloring. The Casket made full of wood, with wooden hardware, no metal parts are added. This casket will fit into most standard ceremony.

**Features:**

 - Mate finish
 - Teak Veneer Wood
 - Ivory velvet interior
 - Cremation Casket: Commonly used for burials
 - Wooden Hardware

**Casket Dimensions:**

 - Exterior: 84L x 28W x 23.5H

 - Interior width: 24"

Weight: 200 pounds
